{"tid":1146080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幼稚園後巷發現貓屍 爆內臟吐血疑遭虐死","createTime":"2019-05-09T04:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T04:57:31.000Z","uid":3090,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a589eff10e5ba8c01b3cb112bacad0f9412bfc9c","tid":1146080,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/svnmxhb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsvnmxhb.png&h=6ef4ac3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上水馬會道23號上水堂幼稚園後巷範圍，早上9時04分，男途人發現一頭短毛貓屍體倒卧地上，全身濕透，臉部淌血有傷痕，懷疑遭虐待致死，報警求助，警員接報到場，並召來愛護動物協會人員協助，正了解其致死原因，警方暫列虐待動物案件處理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該頭豹紋色成年雄性短毛家貓，左前臂有約1吋長傷口，內臟爆裂，口吐血，初步疑受撞擊致死，不排除由高處墮下，或曾被車輛輾過，警員翻看附近cctv，發現清晨5時，短毛貓已伏屍後巷，但不見有人爬入後巷行兇。"},{"pid":"764cee6ad0a4be5c117bbf8bcc5aa478a7288498","tid":1146080,"uid":4736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"MEOW MEOW<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079b0b1b4734793c4837eab585b013db36f1879f","tid":1146080,"uid":225295,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"平時當主人係狗呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cada9f24487da53687be867c402e57a9a0484c9","tid":1146080,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"宜家啲幼稚園學生咁暴力"}]}